WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.050 --> 00:00:01.923
One request can generate code.

2
00:00:01.923 --> 00:00:04.375
Engineering needs a coordinated swarm.

3
00:00:04.375 --> 00:00:09.326
HIVE — Hyper Intelligence for Verified Engineering — puts one Queen at the center.

4
00:00:09.326 --> 00:00:11.262
Scout maps the repository.

5
00:00:11.262 --> 00:00:12.704
