Fixer repairs and revalidates.

10
00:00:19.230 --> 00:00:24.867
In HIVE, TypeScript checking passes, while the latest test limitation remains disclosed.

11
00:00:24.867 --> 00:00:29.170
Pledgr passes 165 tests across 21 files.

12
00:00:29.170 --> 00:00:35.649
TraderBot passes 40 tests across four safety-gated modules, with live trading disabled by default.

13
00:00:35.649 --> 00:00:40.540
Every claim links to a command, repository file, or captured interface.

14
00:00:40.540 --> 00:00:42.067
